room_title: Escape room "The Laboratory" by Escape Room Delaware in Dover
room_description: A deadly virus has broken out in three major cities! The CDC has issued a warning that in an hour, the infection will spread too far to be irreversible. A cure must be developed, and fast! Unfortunately, the lead scientist had a heart attack, and his stuff is all locked up somewhere secret. You have been handed the task of finding all of Dr. Diehardâ€™s work and putting it together to create the antidote.
